  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nCurrently the default beacon node's API namespace are `[\"beacon\", \"config\", \"events\", \"node\", \"validator\"]`. By default a beacon node won't be able to serve light client related data via the rest api \r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nConsider having light client namespace as part of the default namespace. \r\n\r\nPros:\r\n- Improves availability of light client related data. \r\n\r\nCons?\r\n- Serving light client related data might not be considered symbiotic.\r\n",
